{"tid":2132286,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"區諾軒見記者","createTime":"2020-07-30T09:52:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T11:34:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"96406012106efee94e4e60fc19480fd082294998","tid":2132286,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:52:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iQSiVUXsb-Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiQSiVUXsb-Q&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSh4DU%2FdTpVEdsDcTgM8IVTs%3D&h=96aaa8c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iQSiVUXsb-Q</a>"},{"pid":"b7b59e2855601000ebd4dbe99042f135d90e9f98","tid":2132286,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:57:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5d5461594a65c300bba7a4df2dd6d299ee2dab","tid":2132286,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:58:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"341027946585c212fe2cabe6700f60ed34079d55","tid":2132286,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:58:57.000Z","msg":"認罪喎"},{"pid":"f09bcef991eed2059874c229c0c71b310de57526","tid":2132286,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"341027946585c212fe2cabe6700f60ed34079d55","tid":2132286,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T09:58:57.000Z","msg":"認罪喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T11:34:38.000Z","msg":"區諾軒庭外指，選擇認罪是因相信他的戰場不在法庭，而是做一個頂天立地的學者，未來幾年會走學術道路。更重要的是，眼見律政司對他作出的都是荒謬指控，「甚至是惡意的檢控，根本不是講道理，不滿意你做社會服務令，首先在裁判法院上訴，再於上訴庭上訴」，認為做法對社會無益，「如果我嘅人生要再前行，我係唔可以俾律政司阻到我，所以我喺呢單案上，我選擇咗速戰速決」。他尊重同案的戰友繼續抗爭，但坦言已對這個司法制度失去信心，「我選擇咗認罪，食咗呢舊屎佢」。他指，爭取民主的戰線很多，他選擇退後少少。被問到是否擔心判監，他重申無論最後結果如何，只想速戰速決。"}]}